<lb n="0060a13" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0060a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060a15" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1586 [No. 1587; cf. No. 1585]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0060a16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>唯識三十論<note n="0060005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">Triṁśikā vijñaptikārikā.〔頌〕－【三】</note><note n="0060005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">Triṁśikā vijñaptikārikā.，〔頌〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><foreign n="0060005" cb:resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" cb:place="foot">Triṁśikā vijñaptikārikā.</foreign><app n="0060005"><lem wit="【大】">頌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0060a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060a18" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Author">世親菩薩造</byline>
<lb n="0060a19" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0060006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大唐〕－【宋】【元】，〔大〕－【明】</note><app n="0060006"><lem wit="【大】">大唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐</rdg></app>三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0060a20" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT31p0060a2001">護法等菩薩約此三十頌造《成唯識》，今略標
<lb n="0060a21" ed="T"/>所以。謂此三十頌中，初二十四行頌明唯識
<lb n="0060a22" ed="T"/>相；次一行頌明唯識性；後五行頌明唯識行
<lb n="0060a23" ed="T"/>位。就二十四行頌中，初一行半略辯唯識相；
<lb n="0060a24" ed="T"/>次二十二行半廣辯唯識相。謂外問言：「若唯
<lb n="0060a25" ed="T"/>有識，云何世間及諸聖教說有我法？」舉頌<note n="0060007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">詶＝以【明】</note><app n="0060007"><lem wit="【大】">詶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以</rdg></app>
<lb n="0060a26" ed="T"/>答，頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060a27" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060a2701" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><head>「１</head><l>由假說我法，</l><l>有種種相轉。</l>
<lb n="0060a28" ed="T"/><l>彼依<note n="0060008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">識所變 Vijñāna-pariṇāma.</note><cb:tt n="0060008" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">識所變</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vijñāna-pariṇāma.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>此<note n="0060009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能變 Pariṇāma.</note><cb:tt n="0060009" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">能變</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Pariṇāma.</cb:t></cb:tt>唯三：</l></lg>
<lb n="0060a29" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060a2901"><head>２</head><l>謂<note n="0060010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">異熟 Vipāka.</note><cb:tt n="0060010" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">異熟</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vipāka.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">思量 Manana.</note><cb:tt n="0060011" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">思量</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Manana.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>及<note n="0060012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了別境識 Viṣaya-vijñapti.</note><cb:tt n="0060012" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">了別境識</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Viṣaya-vijñapti.</cb:t></cb:tt>。」</l></lg>
<pb n="0060b" xml:id="T31.1586.0060b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0060b0101"><note n="0060013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝此【三】</note><note n="0060013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次＝此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0060013"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">此</rdg></app>二十二行半廣辯唯識相者，由前頌文略
<lb n="0060b02" ed="T"/>標三能變，今廣明三變相。且初能變其相云
<lb n="0060b03" ed="T"/>何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b0401" rend="margin-left:0em"><l>「　初<note n="0060014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">阿賴耶識 Ālaya-vijñāna.</note><cb:tt n="0060014" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">阿賴耶識</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ālaya-vijñāna.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>異熟<note n="0060015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一切種 Sarva-vījaka.</note><cb:tt n="0060015" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">一切種</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sarva-vījaka.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b05" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b0501" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><head>３</head><l><note n="0060016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不可知 Asaṁviditaka.</note><cb:tt n="0060016" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">不可知</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Asaṁviditaka.</cb:t></cb:tt><note n="0060017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">執受 Upādi.</note><cb:tt n="0060017" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">執受</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Upādi.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0060018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處 Sthāna.</note><cb:tt n="0060018" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">處</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sthāna.</cb:t></cb:tt><note n="0060019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了（別） Vijñaptika.</note><note n="0060019" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->了（別） Vijñaptika.</note>了常與<note n="0060020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觸 Sparśa.</note><cb:tt n="0060020" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">觸</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sparśa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b06" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作意 Manaskāra.</note><cb:tt n="0060021" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">作意</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Manaskāra.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受 Vit(vedanā).</note><note n="0060022" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->受 Vit(vedanā).</note>受、<note n="0060023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想 Saṁjñā.</note><cb:tt n="0060023" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">想</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Saṁjñā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">思 Cetanā.</note><cb:tt n="0060024" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">思</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Cetanā.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>相應唯<note n="0060025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 Upekṣā.</note><cb:tt n="0060025" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">捨</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Upekṣā.</cb:t></cb:tt>受。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b0701" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><head>４</head><l>是<note n="0060026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無覆無記 Artivṛtyākṛta.</note><cb:tt n="0060026" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">無覆無記</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Artivṛtyākṛta.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>觸等亦如是，</l>
<lb n="0060b08" ed="T"/><l>恒轉如<note n="0060027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瀑＝暴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0060027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瀑＝暴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0060027"><lem wit="【大】">瀑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">暴</rdg></app>流，</l><l>阿羅漢位<note n="0060028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 Vyāvṛtti.</note><cb:tt n="0060028" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">捨</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vyāvṛtti.</cb:t></cb:tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0060b0901">已說初能變，第二能變其相<note n="0060029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＝去【明】</note><app n="0060029"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去</rdg></app>何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b1001" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><head>「５</head><l>次第二能變，</l><l>是識名<note n="0060030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末那 Manas.</note><cb:tt n="0060030" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">末那</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Manas.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0060b11" ed="T"/><l>依彼轉緣彼，</l><l>思量為性相。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b12" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b1201" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><head>６</head><l>四煩惱常俱，</l><l>謂<note n="0060031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我癡 Ātma-moha.</note><cb:tt n="0060031" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">我癡</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ātma-moha.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我見 Ātma-dṛṣṭi.</note><cb:tt n="0060032" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">我見</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ātma-dṛṣṭi.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b13" ed="T"/><l>并<note n="0060033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我慢 Ātma-māna.</note><cb:tt n="0060033" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">我慢</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ātma-māna.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我愛 Ātma-sneha.</note><cb:tt n="0060034" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">我愛</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ātma-sneha.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>及餘觸等俱。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b14" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b1401" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><head>７</head><l><note n="0060035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">有覆無記 Nivrtāvyākrta.</note><cb:tt n="0060035" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">有覆無記</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Nivrtāvyākrta.</cb:t></cb:tt>攝，</l><l>隨所生所繫，</l>
<lb n="0060b15" ed="T"/><l>阿羅漢<note n="0060036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滅定 Nirodha-samāpatti.</note><cb:tt n="0060036" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">滅定</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Nirodha-samāpatti.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0060037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">出世道 Lokottara-mārga.</note><cb:tt n="0060037" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">出世道</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Lokottara-mārga.</cb:t></cb:tt>無有。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0060b1601">如是已說第二能變，第三能變其相云何？頌
<lb n="0060b17" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0060b18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b1801" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><head>「８</head><l>次第三能變，</l><l>差別有六種，</l>
<lb n="0060b19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了境 Viṣaya-upalabdhi.</note><cb:tt n="0060038" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">了境</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Viṣaya-upalabdhi.</cb:t></cb:tt>為性相，</l><l>善不善俱非。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b20" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b2001" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-1em"><head>９</head><l>此<note n="0060039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心所 Caitasa.</note><cb:tt n="0060039" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">心所</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Caitasa.</cb:t></cb:tt><note n="0060040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍行 Sarvatraga.</note><cb:tt n="0060040" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">遍行</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sarvatraga.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">別境 Viniyata.</note><cb:tt n="0060041" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">別境</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Viniyata.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善 Kuśala.</note><cb:tt n="0060042" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">善</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Kuśala.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">煩惱 Kleśa.</note><cb:tt n="0060043" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">煩惱</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Kleśa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b21" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隨煩惱 Upakleśa.</note><cb:tt n="0060044" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">隨煩惱</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Upakleśa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、不定，</l><l>皆三受相應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b22" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１０</head><l>初遍行觸等，</l><l>次別境謂<note n="0060045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欲 Chanda.</note><cb:tt n="0060045" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">欲</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Chanda.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l>
<lb n="0060b23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勝解 Abhimokṣa.</note><cb:tt n="0060046" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">勝解</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Abhimokṣa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念 Smṛti.</note><cb:tt n="0060047" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">念</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Smṛti.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">定 Samādhi.</note><cb:tt n="0060048" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">定</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Samādhi.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慧 Dhī(prajñā).</note><note n="0060049" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->慧 Dhī(prajñā).</note>慧，</l><l>所緣事不同。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b2401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１１</head><l>善謂<note n="0060050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">信 Śraddhā.</note><cb:tt n="0060050" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">信</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Śraddhā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慚 Hrī.</note><cb:tt n="0060051" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">慚</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Hrī.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愧 Apatrapā.</note><cb:tt n="0060052" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">愧</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Apatrapā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無貪 Alobha，無瞋 Adveśa，無癡 Amoha.</note>無貪等三根，</l>
<lb n="0060b25" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">勤 Vīrya.</note><cb:tt n="0060054" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">勤</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vīrya.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安（輕安） Praśrabdhi.</note><note n="0060055" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->安（輕安） Praśrabdhi.</note>安、<note n="0060056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不放逸行 Apramāda.</note><note n="0060056" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->不放逸行 Apramāda.</note>不放逸、</l><l>行<note n="0060057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨 (upekṣā)</note><cb:tt n="0060057" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">捨</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">(upekṣā)</cb:t></cb:tt>及<note n="0060058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不害 Ahiṁsā.</note><cb:tt n="0060058" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">不害</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Ahiṁsā.</cb:t></cb:tt>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b26" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b2601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１２</head><l>煩惱謂<note n="0060059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">貪 Rāga.</note><cb:tt n="0060059" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">貪</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Rāga.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瞋 Pratigha.</note><cb:tt n="0060060" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">瞋</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Pratigha.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">癡 Mūḍha.</note><cb:tt n="0060061" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">癡</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mūḍha.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慢 Māna.</note><cb:tt n="0060062" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">慢</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Māna.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">疑 Vicikitsā.</note><cb:tt n="0060063" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">疑</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vicikitsā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惡見 Dṛś(mithyā dṛṣṭi).</note><note n="0060064" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->惡見 Dṛś(mithyā dṛṣṭi).</note>惡見。</l>
<lb n="0060b27" ed="T"/><l>隨煩惱謂<note n="0060065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忿 Krodha.</note><cb:tt n="0060065" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">忿</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Krodha.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恨 Upanāha.</note><cb:tt n="0060066" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">恨</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Upanāha.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覆 Mrakṣa.</note><cb:tt n="0060067" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">覆</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mrakṣa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惱 Pradāśa.</note><cb:tt n="0060068" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">惱</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Pradāśa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嫉 IIṛṣyā.</note><note n="0060069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嫉<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>Iṛṣyā</corr><sic> IIṛṣyā</sic></choice>.</note><cb:tt n="0060069" type="app"><cb:t resp="CBETA" xml:lang="zh">嫉</cb:t><cb:t resp="CBETA" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Iṛṣyā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慳 Mātsarya.</note><cb:tt n="0060070" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">慳</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mātsarya.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l></lg>
<lb n="0060b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060b2801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１３</head><l><note n="0060071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誑 Śāṭhya.</note><cb:tt n="0060071" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">誑</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Śāṭhya.</cb:t></cb:tt><note n="0060072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諂 (māyā).</note>、<cb:tt n="0060072" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">諂</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">(māyā).</cb:t></cb:tt>與<note n="0060073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">害 Vihiṁsā.</note><cb:tt n="0060073" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">害</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vihiṁsā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">憍 Mada.</note><cb:tt n="0060074" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">憍</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mada.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060075" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無慚 Āhrī(āhrīkya).</note><note n="0060075" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->無慚 Āhrī(āhrīkya).</note>無慚及<note n="0060076" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無愧 Atrapā(anapatrapāya).</note><note n="0060076" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->無愧 Atrapā(anapatrapāya).</note>無愧、</l>
<lb n="0060b29" ed="T"/><l><note n="0060077" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掉舉 Auddhatya.</note><cb:tt n="0060077" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">掉舉</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Auddhatya.</cb:t></cb:tt>與<note n="0060078" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惛＝昏【三】【宮】，惛沈 Styāna.</note><note n="0060078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惛沈 Styāna.，惛＝昏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><cb:tt n="0060078" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh"><app n="0060078"><lem wit="【大】">惛沈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">昏沈</rdg></app></cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Styāna.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060079" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不信 Āśraddhya.</note><cb:tt n="0060079" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">不信</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Āśraddhya.</cb:t></cb:tt>并<note n="0060080" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懈怠 Kauśīdya.</note><cb:tt n="0060080" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">懈怠</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Kauśīdya.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l></lg>
<pb n="0060c" xml:id="T31.1586.0060c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0060c01" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060c0101" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１４</head><l><note n="0060081" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">放逸 Pramāda.</note><cb:tt n="0060081" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">放逸</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Pramāda.</cb:t></cb:tt>及<note n="0060082" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">失念 Muṣṭa-smṛṭati.</note><cb:tt n="0060082" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">失念</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Muṣṭa-smṛṭati.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0060083" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散亂 Vikṣepa.</note><cb:tt n="0060083" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">散亂</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vikṣepa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060084" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不正知 Asamprajanya.</note><cb:tt n="0060084" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">不正知</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Asamprajanya.</cb:t></cb:tt>。</l>
<lb n="0060c02" ed="T"/><l>不定謂<note n="0060085" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悔（惡作） Kaukṛtya.</note><note n="0060085" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->悔（惡作） Kaukṛtya.</note>悔、<note n="0060086" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眠 Middha.</note><cb:tt n="0060086" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">眠</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Middha.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0060087" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尋 Vitarka.</note><cb:tt n="0060087" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">尋</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vitarka.</cb:t></cb:tt>、<note n="0060088" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">伺 Vicāra.</note><cb:tt n="0060088" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">伺</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vicāra.</cb:t></cb:tt>二各二。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0060c0301">已說六識心所相應，云何應知現起分位？頌
<lb n="0060c04" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0060c05" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060c0501" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「１５</head><l>依止<note n="0060089" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">根本識 Mūla-vijñāna</note><cb:tt n="0060089" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">根本識</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mūla-vijñāna</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>五識隨緣現，</l>
<lb n="0060c06" ed="T"/><l>或俱或不俱，</l><l>如濤波依水。</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0060c0701" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>１６</head><l><note n="0060090" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意識 Manas.</note><cb:tt n="0060090" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">意識</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Manas.</cb:t></cb:tt>常現起，</l><l>除生<note n="0060091" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無想天 Āsaṁjñika.</note><cb:tt n="0060091" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">無想天</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Āsaṁjñika.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0060c08" ed="T"/><l>及<note n="0060092" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無心二定（無想定） Asaṁjñi-samāpatti.（滅盡定） nirodha-samāpatti.</note>無心二定，</l><l><note n="0060093" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">睡眠 (acittaka).</note><cb:tt n="0060093" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">睡眠</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">(acittaka).</cb:t></cb:tt>與<note n="0060094" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悶絕 Mūrcchā.</note><cb:tt n="0060094" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">悶絕</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Mūrcchā.</cb:t></cb:tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0060c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0060c0901">已廣分別三能變相為自所變二分所依，云
<lb n="0060c10" ed="T"/>何應知依識所變假說我、法非別實有，<note n="0060095" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">由＝猶【三】</note><note n="0060095" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＝猶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0060095"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">猶</rdg></app>斯
<pb n="0061a" xml:id="T31.1586.0061a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0061a01" ed="T"/>一切唯有識耶？頌<note n="0061001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0061001"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0061a02" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a0201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「１７</head><l>是諸識轉變，</l><l><note n="0061002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分別 Vikalpa.</note><cb:tt n="0061002" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">分別</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vikalpa.</cb:t></cb:tt>、所分別，</l>
<lb n="0061a03" ed="T"/><l>由此彼皆無，</l><l>故一切<note n="0061003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯識 Vijñapti-mātraka.</note><cb:tt n="0061003" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">唯識</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vijñapti-mātraka.</cb:t></cb:tt>。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061a0401">若唯有識，都無外緣，由何而生種種分別？頌
<lb n="0061a05" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a06" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a0601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「１８</head><l>由一切種識，</l><l>如是如是變，</l>
<lb n="0061a07" ed="T"/><l>以<note n="0061004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">展轉力 Anyo'nyavaśa.</note><cb:tt n="0061004" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">展轉力</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Anyo'nyavaśa.</cb:t></cb:tt>故，</l><l>彼彼分別生。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061a0801">雖有內識而無外緣，由何有情生死相續？頌
<lb n="0061a09" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a1001" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「１９</head><l>由諸<note n="0061005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">業習氣 Karma-vāśanā.</note><cb:tt n="0061005" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">業習氣</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Karma-vāśanā.</cb:t></cb:tt>、</l><l><note n="0061006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二取 Grāhadvaya（我執習氣 grāhya-grāha，名言習氣 grāhaka-grāha）.</note>二取習氣俱，</l>
<lb n="0061a11" ed="T"/><l>前異熟既盡，</l><l>復生餘異熟。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061a1201">若唯有識，何故世尊處處經中說有三性？應
<lb n="0061a13" ed="T"/>知三性亦不離識，所以者何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a14" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a1401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２０</head><l>由彼彼遍計，</l><l>遍計種種物，</l>
<lb n="0061a15" ed="T"/><l>此<note n="0061007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍計所執 Parikalpita.</note><cb:tt n="0061007" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">遍計所執</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Parikalpita.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0061008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自性 Svabhāva.</note><cb:tt n="0061008" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">自性</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Svabhāva.</cb:t></cb:tt>無所有。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a16" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a1601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>２１</head><l><note n="0061009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依他起自性 Paratantra-svabhāva.</note><cb:tt n="0061009" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">依他起自性</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Paratantra-svabhāva.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0061010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">分別緣所生 Vikalpaḥ pratyayodbhavaḥ.</note><cb:tt n="0061010" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">分別緣所生</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Vikalpaḥ pratyayodbhavaḥ.</cb:t></cb:tt>。</l>
<lb n="0061a17" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">圓成實性 Niṣpanna(pariniṣpanna).</note><note n="0061011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: u-->圓成實性 Niṣpanna(pariniṣpanna).</note>圓成實於彼，</l><l>常遠離前性。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a1801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>２２</head><l>故此與依他，</l><l>非異非不異，</l>
<lb n="0061a19" ed="T"/><l>如無常等性，</l><l><note n="0061012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">非不見此彼 （コレヲミズシテカレチミルモノニアラズ）Nādṛṣṭe asmin(pariniṣpanne)sa (paratantra-svabhāvo)dṛśyate.</note>非不見此彼。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061a2001">若有三性，如何世尊說一切法皆無自性？頌
<lb n="0061a21" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0061a22" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２３</head><l>即依此三性，</l><l>立彼<note n="0061013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三無性 Trividhā niḥsvabhāvatā.</note><cb:tt n="0061013" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">三無性</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Trividhā niḥsvabhāvatā.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a23" ed="T"/><l>故佛密意說，</l><l><note n="0061014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一切法無性 Sarva-dharmānāṁ niḥsvabhāvatā.</note><cb:tt n="0061014" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">一切法無性</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sarva-dharmānāṁ niḥsvabhāvatā.</cb:t></cb:tt>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a2401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>２４</head><l>初即<note n="0061015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相 Lakṣaṇa.</note><cb:tt n="0061015" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">相</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Lakṣaṇa.</cb:t></cb:tt>無性，</l><l>次無<note n="0061016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自然性 Svayaṁbhāva.</note><cb:tt n="0061016" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">自然性</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Svayaṁbhāva.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a25" ed="T"/><l>後由遠離前，</l><l>所執我、法性。</l></lg>
<lb n="0061a26" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061a2601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-2em"><head>２５</head><l>此<note n="0061017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諸法勝義 Dharmānām paramārtha.</note><cb:tt n="0061017" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">諸法勝義</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Dharmānām paramārtha.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>亦即是<note n="0061018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">真如 Tathatā.</note><cb:tt n="0061018" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">真如</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Tathatā.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061a27" ed="T"/><note n="0061019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當如其性故即唯識實性 Sarvakā'aṁ tathābhāvāt saiva vijñaptimātratā.</note><note n="0061019" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><choice cb:resp="CBETA.say"><corr>常</corr><sic>當</sic></choice>如其性故即唯識實性 Sarvakā'aṁ tathābhāvāt saiva vijñaptimātratā.</note><cb:tt n="0061019" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh"><l>常如其性故，</l><l>即唯識實性。」</l></cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sarvakā'aṁ tathābhāvāt saiva vijñaptimātratā.</cb:t></cb:tt></lg>
<lb n="0061a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061a2801">後<note n="0061020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝三【元】【明】</note><app n="0061020"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>行頌明唯識行位者，論曰：「如是所成唯
<lb n="0061a29" ed="T"/>識性、相，誰依幾位？如何悟入？」謂具大乘二種
<pb n="0061b" xml:id="T31.1586.0061b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0061b01" ed="T"/>種性：一、本性種性，謂無始來依附本識，法爾
<lb n="0061b02" ed="T"/>所得無漏法因；二、謂習所成種性，謂聞法界
<lb n="0061b03" ed="T"/>等流法已，聞所成<note n="0061021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔等薰習所成〕－【三】</note><note n="0061021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔等<choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>熏</corr><sic>薰</sic></choice>習所成〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061021"><lem wit="【大】">等熏習所成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。具此二性
<lb n="0061b04" ed="T"/>方能悟入。何謂五位？一、資糧位，謂修大乘順
<lb n="0061b05" ed="T"/>解脫分，依識性、相能深信解。其相云何？頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0061b06" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061b0601" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２６</head><l>乃至未起識，</l><l>求住唯識性，</l>
<lb n="0061b07" ed="T"/><l>於二取隨眠，</l><l><note n="0061022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">Yāvad vijñapti-mātratve vijñānaṁ nāvatiṣṭhati | grāhadvayasyānuśayas tāvan vini vartate ||</note><foreign n="0061022" cb:resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" cb:place="foot">Yāvad vijñapti-mātratve vijñānaṁ nāvatiṣṭhati | grāhadvayasyānuśayas tāvan vini vartate ||</foreign>猶未能伏滅。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061b0801">二、加行位，謂修大乘順決擇分，在加行<note n="0061023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">位＝謂【三】</note><note n="0061023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">位＝謂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061023"><lem wit="【大】">位</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">謂</rdg></app>能
<lb n="0061b09" ed="T"/>漸伏除所取、能取。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061b1001" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２７</head><l>現前立少物，</l><l>謂是唯識性，</l>
<lb n="0061b11" ed="T"/><l>以有所得故，</l><l>非實住唯識。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061b1201">三、通達位，謂諸菩薩所<note n="0061024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝位【三】</note><note n="0061024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝位【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0061024"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">位</rdg></app>見道，在通達位如
<lb n="0061b13" ed="T"/>實通達。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b14" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061b1401" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２８</head><note n="0061025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若時於所緣智都無所得 Yadā tv ālambanaṁ vijñānaṁ naivopalabhate tadā.</note><cb:tt n="0061025" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh"><l rend="margin-left:0em">若時於所緣，</l><l>智都無所得，</l></cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Yadā tv ālambanaṁ vijñānaṁ naivopalabhate tadā.</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0061b15" ed="T"/><l>爾時住唯識，</l><l>離二取相故。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061b1601">四、修習位，謂諸菩薩所住修道，修習位中如
<lb n="0061b17" ed="T"/>實見理，數數修習。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061b1801" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「２９</head><note n="0061026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無得不思議 Acintyo'nupalambhaḥ</note><l><cb:tt n="0061026" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">無得不思議</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Acintyo'nupalambhaḥ</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>是<note n="0061027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">出世間智 Lakottara-jñāna.</note><cb:tt n="0061027" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">出世間智</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Lakottara-jñāna.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061b19" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨麁重 Dauṣṭhulyahāni.</note>捨二麁重故，</l><l>便證得<note n="0061029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉依 Āśrayasya parāvṛttiḥ （變住 mvp. 131）</note>轉依。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0061b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT31p0061b2001">五、究竟位，謂住無上正等菩提，出障圓明，能
<lb n="0061b21" ed="T"/>盡未來化有情類。其相云何？</p>
<lb n="0061b22" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT31p0061b2201" rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-3em"><head>「３０</head><l>此即<note n="0061030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無漏界 Anāśravī dhātuḥ.</note><cb:tt n="0061030" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">無漏界</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Anāśravī dhātuḥ.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l>不思議<note n="0061031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善 Kuśala.</note><cb:tt n="0061031" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">善</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Kuśala.</cb:t></cb:tt><note n="0061032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常 Dhruva.</note><cb:tt n="0061032" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">常</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Dhruva.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l>
<lb n="0061b23" ed="T"/><l><note n="0061033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安樂解脫身 Sukhīvimukti-kāyaḥ.</note><cb:tt n="0061033" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">安樂解脫身</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Sukhīvimukti-kāyaḥ.</cb:t></cb:tt>，</l><l><note n="0061034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大牟尼名法 Dharmākhyo 'yam mahāmuneḥ.</note><cb:tt n="0061034" type="app"><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="zh">大牟尼名法</cb:t><cb:t resp="Taisho" xml:lang="sa" place="foot">Dharmākhyo 'yam mahāmuneḥ.</cb:t></cb:tt>。」</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0061b24" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>唯識三十論頌</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
